introPara1: Years of experience ... is a phrase consists of three words, but when it is attached to The Times Press, it is a reminder of decades of hard work and proud memories.
introPara2: These past golden years is squeezed into the word YESTERDAY for us as we NOW stand on top of excellent results and looking towards the FUTURE.
introPara3: Today we are known as the ISO certified leading offset printing concern in Pakistan, with our capabilities, years of experience and the equipment that matters.
